The paper discusses the use of machine learning methods for drug discovery, which falls under the category of computational biology and bioinformatics. The paper specifically focuses on the validation and benchmarking of these methods, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
